{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/group"]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@frozen","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Group","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"Content","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use a group to collect multiple views into a single instance, without"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"affecting the layout of those views, like an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HStack"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OpenSwiftUI\/Section"},{"type":"text","text":" would. After creating a group,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"any modifier you apply to the group affects all of that group’s members."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, the following code applies the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Font\/headline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"font to three views in a group."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["Group {","    Text(\"OpenSwiftUI\")","    Text(\"Combine\")","    Text(\"Swift System\")","}",".font(.headline)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Because you create a group of views with a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ViewBuilder","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", you can","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use the group’s initializer to produce different kinds of views from a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conditional, and then optionally apply modifiers to them. The following","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"example uses a ","type":"text"},{"code":"Group","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to add a navigation bar title,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"regardless of the type of view the conditional produces:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["Group {","    if isLoggedIn {","        WelcomeView()","    } else {","        LoginView()","    }","}",".navigationBarTitle(\"Start\")"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The modifier applies to all members of the group — and not to the group","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"itself. For example, if you apply ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View\/onAppear(perform:)"},{"text":" to the above","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"group, it applies to all of the views produced by the ","type":"text"},{"code":"if isLoggedIn","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conditional, and it executes every time ","type":"text"},{"code":"isLoggedIn","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" changes.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because a group of views itself is a view, you can compose a group within"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other view builders, including nesting within other groups. This allows you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to add large numbers of views to different view builder containers. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"following example uses a "},{"code":"Group","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to collect 10 "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" instances,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"meaning that the vertical stack’s view builder returns only two views —"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the group, plus an additional "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["var body: some View {","    VStack {","        Group {","            Text(\"1\")","            Text(\"2\")","            Text(\"3\")","            Text(\"4\")","            Text(\"5\")","            Text(\"6\")","            Text(\"7\")","            Text(\"8\")","            Text(\"9\")","            Text(\"10\")","        }","        Text(\"11\")","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can initialize groups with several types other than ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Scene","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"OpenSwiftUI\/ToolbarContent","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". The closure you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provide to the group initializer uses the corresponding builder type","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/SceneBuilder","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"OpenSwiftUI\/ToolbarContentBuilder","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and so on),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and the capabilities of these builders vary between types. For example,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you can use groups to return large numbers of scenes or toolbar content","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"instances, but not to return different scenes or toolbar content based","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on conditionals.","type":"text"}]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that collects multiple instances of a content type — like views,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"scenes, or commands — into a single unit."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","title":"Group","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore5GroupV","symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Group","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Group","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":[{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS"},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"10.15","beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"macOS"},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS"},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS"},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"6.0","beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/View\/Group.swift#L85","fileName":"Group.swift"},"role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View"],"kind":"relationships"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Group","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"a